  "2026-02-18T22:01:25.957Z",cursor-maintainer,"Docs-first alignment applied: README and PRD now treat pm reindex as implemented keyword-cache baseline, while semantic/vector reindex behavior remains roadmap. Updated command matrix/output contract and milestone wording accordingly before code changes."
